cat /tmp/dexter-operator-ready-install.out
pass "Dock launcher installed"

cat <<'TEXT'

Dexter operator readiness complete.

Start Dexter:
  open "$HOME/Applications/Dexter.app"

Or from this repo:
  make run

After Dexter is running:
  make status

To inspect saved acceptance evidence:
